  <name>IPlan</name>
  <summary>Your plan for improve personal life and workflow</summary>
  <description>
    <p>IPlan goal is to be a user friendly tool for who wants to organize his personal life or jobs.</p>
	  <p>Features:</p>
	  <ul>
	    <li>Grouping tasks with project and list</li>
	    <li>Timer for tasks</li>
	    <li>Global search</li>
	    <li>Arranging projects, lists and tasks by drag and drop</li>
	  </ul>
	</description>
